FBIS4-14504 "drsov063_g_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-063 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Issuing of Privatization Vouchers Begins 1 Apr Issuing of Privatization Vouchers Begins 1 Apr WS0104112494 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1000 GMT 1 Apr 94 WS0104112494 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Belarusian BFN [Text] The amount of state property to be handed over to Belarusian citizens will be based on their age and length of work. The issuing of privatization vouchers has begun today in the Republic. Beginning 1 July, people will be able to purchase stocks, using the vouchers for payments. It has taken almost one year for specialists to work out a mechanism for implementing privatization.
